{"tid":1386714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家 由今日開始 想做善事嘅請先集中幫左香港班義士先","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T20:02:49.000Z","uid":152630,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad7dd4597579e1724856807e64a747afe082445","tid":1386714,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"我夠膽講十年八年內 香港最需要幫手嘅就係一班年輕嘅學生義士 同埋自由嘅獨立媒體 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">前線嘅勇武義士係香港人最強嘅武器 而獨立嘅記者媒體就係守護真相嘅最後一道防線</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再捐畀公益金東華聯合國之類既大型又要收行政費嘅所謂慈善團體 要幫一定係<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人優先</span><br />\n 大家有錢出錢有力出力 我哋呢個世代真係要靠團結先可以同不義政權作最後一搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"d008bcbfa770041c86e027ffa9742a59112e3414","tid":1386714,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:24.000Z","msg":"不分化，各有各做。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a7d0020a24bb68d29bbf7a3b8abd303a0e98181","tid":1386714,"uid":152630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"14ebd5272cca0aa6236f664f475b7d5b090aa5f5","tid":1386714,"uid":152630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9f3f43c8cf4b6e0cd10720da06aa46bb5482c42d","tid":1386714,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"267cd075e75306ebf15eddb175061597b6fb13a2","tid":1386714,"uid":152630